{"parentUuid":"969e48a0-6338-4f23-a53f-bd367ee4eb8b","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\TmRobot Ex","sessionId":"3730fa05-1fd7-4481-b70e-b109a897690f","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"HEAD","agentId":"abc44ae20508b5180","slug":"radiant-hatching-hopcroft","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SW9CfizgDccg3YKvMHiR6i","type":"tool_result","content":"   195→## 5. 타입 변환\n   196→\n   197→### 명시적 캐스팅\n   198→\n   199→```\n   200→(int)100      // byte → int\n   201→(float)100    // byte → float\n   202→(double)3.14  // float → double\n   203→```\n   204→\n   205→### 암묵적 변환 규칙\n   206→- 더 작은 타입 → 더 큰 타입으로 자동 승격\n   207→- byte → int → float → double 순서\n   208→\n   209→---"}]},"uuid":"2b1efe8c-78e6-40b8-9130-f57cc192a3b3","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:03:39.312Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"969e48a0-6338-4f23-a53f-bd367ee4eb8b"}
{"parentUuid":"2b1efe8c-78e6-40b8-9130-f57cc192a3b3","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\TmRobot Ex","sessionId":"3730fa05-1fd7-4481-b70e-b109a897690f","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"HEAD","agentId":"abc44ae20508b5180","slug":"radiant-hatching-hopcroft","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LrDDThfVBWe8KCYaMNcHB1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"확인 완료. 결과를 정리합니다.\n\n---\n\n## 답변\n\n### 1. string -> int 변환: `String_ToInteger()`\n\nTMscript에는 `CInt()` 함수가 **없습니다**. 정확한 함수명은 다음과 같습니다.\n\n```\nint String_ToInteger(string s)\nint String_ToInteger(string s, int startIndex)\nint String_ToInteger(string s, int startIndex, int count)\n```\n\n10진수, 16진수(`0x` prefix), 2진수(`0b` prefix) 지원.\n\n### 2. string -> float 변환: `String_ToFloat()`\n\n```\nfloat String_ToFloat(string s)\nfloat String_ToFloat(string s, int startIndex)\nfloat String_ToFloat(string s, int startIndex, int count)\n```\n\n`String_ToDouble()`도 있음 (double 반환).\n\n### 3. 문자열 함수 지원 여부\n\n모두 TMscript에서 **정식 지원**됩니다.\n\n| 함수 | 시그니처 |\n|------|---------|\n| `String_Split` | `string[] String_Split(string source, string delimiter)` |\n| `String_Substring` | `string String_Substring(string source, int startIndex)` |\n| `String_IndexOf` | `int String_IndexOf(string source, string search)` |\n| `String_Replace` | `string String_Replace(string source, string old, string newStr)` |\n| `String_Trim` | `string String_Trim(string source)` |\n\n### 4. 배열 인덱싱 `tokens[0]` 문법\n\n문법 자체는 **맞습니다**. TMscript 배열은 0부터 시작하며 `[]` 연산자로 접근합니다.\n\n```\nstring[] tokens = String_Split(\"100,200,300\", \",\")\n// tokens[0] = \"100\", tokens[1] = \"200\", tokens[2] = \"300\"\n```\n\n### 수정 예시\n\n기존 (에러):\n```\nstring[] tokens = String_Split(data, \",\")\nint val = CInt(tokens[0])          // Error 00048202 - CInt 없음\n```\n\n수정 후:\n```\nstring[] tokens = String_Split(data, \",\")\nint val = String_ToInteger(tokens[0])   // 정상\nfloat fval = String_ToFloat(tokens[1])  // float 필요 시\n```\n\n### 참고: `(int)` 캐스팅과의 차이\n\n`(int)` 캐스팅은 **숫자 타입 간 변환**에만 사용됩니다 (byte->int, float->int 등). **string -> int 변환은 반드시 `String_ToInteger()`를 사용**해야 합니다."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":304,"cache_read_input_tokens":25441,"output_tokens":767,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":304,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYdWbUhBHDvVJrKk6n2g9","type":"assistant","uuid":"4d7ff69a-11c0-4e03-9e1e-f4a3a1d9e3e9","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:03:52.043Z"}
